# DraftLab — what NOT to upload to Vercel.
# Vercel only needs the Next.js project in web/. The data/ folder is a
# Python ingestion + stats pipeline that's run locally; the only output that
# matters to the deployed app (stats.json, champion_meta.json) is already
# copied into web/public/ by run_pipeline.py.

# Big binary artifacts from the local pipeline
data/matches.db
data/matches.db-journal
data/__pycache__/
data/venv/

# Python source (not run on Vercel)
data/*.py
data/_reference/

# Local-only secrets
data/.env
.env
.env.local

# Generated docs / scratch
*.log
*.bak
